room_title: Escape room "Undead Outbreak" by Break Out Myrtle Beach in Myrtle Beach
review: we looooved this!!! As locals, original fun stuff to do is hard to find, but the Zombie room was awesome and Sierra aka "Sprite" was a doll baby, super informative and helpful :) we already have a group coming back in 4days!

room_title: Escape room "Undead Outbreak" by Break Out Myrtle Beach in Myrtle Beach
review: My son, daughter and their friends had a body doing the Zombie Breakout! We will definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "Undead Outbreak" by Break Out Myrtle Beach in Myrtle Beach
review: Our family of 4 had a great time escaping from zombies and finding the cure! It was our first escape room experience. We enjoyed it so much, we immediately did a 2nd one! The clues were hard, but not too hard. The puzzles were well thought out. Just an overall great time!
